<br>
I think this question is kinda an un-question.<br>
You know, like, &quot;why is green?&quot;.<br>
<br>
Religions are not philosophies about what is good for society. No religion is. Religions have been USED by those in power as propaganda for what THEY believe is good for society. Thus all the blodshed in the name of Christ and the one known by names such as &quot;I AM&quot;, Jehova, God and Allah.<br>
<br>
If we want to discuss what's good for society, then lets start talking about Utilitarism, Libertarianism, Kant and Rawls Theory of Justice. Please leave religion out of that subject.<br>
<br>
Just IMHO. <p>Love, Edeina<br>
